</nav></header><main aria-label="main content"><div class="speakable">
      <b data-is-speakable>Harvey Weinstein Verdict: Guilty Of 2 Of 5 Counts In Sex Assault Trial</b>   <b data-is-speakable>Jurors in Manhattan spared the 67-year-old former producer the harshest penalty he might have faced but convicted him on two out of five counts. He faces the possibility of decades in prison.</b>
