                        <h3 class="slug"><a href="https://www.npr.org/sections/law/">Law </a></h3>
            <h3><a href="https://www.npr.org/2020/02/11/804584532/that-never-happened-the-key-moments-during-harvey-weinstein-s-defense"  data-metrics='{"category":"Story to Story","action":"Click Internal Link","label":"https:\/\/www.npr.org\/2020\/02\/11\/804584532\/that-never-happened-the-key-moments-during-harvey-weinstein-s-defense"}' >'That Never Happened': The Key Moments During Harvey Weinstein's Defense</a></h3>
         </div>
         
